    <date day="26" month="February" year="1999"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document provides a printer industry standard SNMP MIB for (1) monitoring the status and progress of print jobs (2) obtaining resource requirements before a job is processed, (3) monitoring resource consumption while a job is being processed and (4) collecting resource accounting data after the completion of a job.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.</t>
    </abstract>
